      "options": {
        "content": "## Budget Variance Tracking\nCompares estimated vs actual time spent on issues (from Jira time tracking).\n\n**Formula:** `Variance % = ((Estimated - Actual) / Estimated) × 100`\n\n| Variance | Interpretation |\n|----------|----------------|\n| Positive | Under budget (faster than estimated) |\n| Zero | On budget |\n| Negative | Over budget (took longer than estimated) |\n\n**Goal:** Track estimation accuracy to improve future planning.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": "mysql",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            { "color": "red", "value": null },
            { "color": "yellow", "value": -10 },
            { "color": "green", "value": 0 }
          ]},
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 60 },
